            [1] = {
                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["body"] = "<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/10-商业化-商店上新.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52); font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>全新配色足迹特效、光晕上架棱镜商店</strong></span></p>\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FvxodE7GWo0yBoxpoROcegBJnsg\"><strong>【上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UotpdOBLwo82mDxERppcncEOnAE\">2025年11月25日 10:00</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QXnKdV2MvodlWqxqflvcX9GmnQO\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-OxJidbFN0oNLCQx8Y7Jc3RY5nEg\"><strong>【售卖说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Etz1d35oVol6A4xbbKWcqucznmo\">在本次更新后，棱镜商店将上新以下内容：</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-RD2AdKC56olhTqxeXuDcD9dwnMg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>光晕：</strong>「夏夜邀约&middot;锈红」「夏夜邀约&middot;涅白」「夏夜邀约&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MmHgdtpdeosFY0xTpbkcsBMAngf\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>足迹特效</strong>：「摇曳轨迹&middot;锈红」「摇曳轨迹&middot;涅白」「摇曳轨迹&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W9O9dBGRioMnCqxhkXvcEoTonvd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YN4sdnC8VoQpFIx1x8fcZUtNnmg\">【其他说明】</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X9ecdwOdToNbPLxYfWPc6et6nMb\">由于本次为棱镜商店首次上新，且公告时间与商店更新间隔较短，为优化各位狩月人的游戏体验，我们将在版本更新后，通过游戏内邮件为此前兑换过原色版本「夏夜邀约」或原色版本「摇曳轨迹」的狩月人，返还其对应消耗的「虹色棱镜」。返还邮件预计在版本更新一周内陆续送达。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JibrdN4jZojdLnx9wFUcCCTZngh\">举例说明：如某狩月人在11月25日前兑换了原色版本「夏夜邀约」与「摇曳轨迹」，版本更新后将收到虹色棱镜*12的返还邮件。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\">未来，棱镜商店将根据大家的反馈持续扩充与上新，每次上新前均会提前发布公告，敬请留意。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-LNG7do76ToBBWQxyAoKcNSn1nbe\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(248, 153, 52);\"><strong>【外观形象装饰】新品上架</strong></span></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SuGSdHxn7oQkNHxnZTmc2QyfnAh\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZBctdnwZvoExrTxdT61c0PG7nvg\"><strong>【上架时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-E9HMdXrztoUxtRxIXOkcP0Axn7d\">2025年11月25日 10:00</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LNhldyJcYoL1yvxq3sDcEQaLnAg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-NfIldKoNgo5F0dxifIVc0jkKnZf\"><strong>【售卖说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ThD3dnV1sovpf7xllEoc8u1FnUh\">在本次更新后，外观商店将上新以下内容</div>\n<ul class=\"list-bullet1\">\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YZyhdtRX9oypn8xqoMmctFacnyh\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>武器形象：</strong>「重剑-群星之焰」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Z2gvdC8U8owuWWxEPdJc0o23nWb\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>腰部配饰：</strong>「玩偶的童话」「玩偶的童话&middot;墨玉」「玩偶的童话&middot;白樱」「玩偶的童话&middot;晴蓝」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-XRIydLzF2ot1CaxN1agcjhXtnvg\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>头部配饰：</strong>「梦中的夜莺」「梦中的夜莺&middot;涅白」「梦中的夜莺&middot;白樱」「梦中的夜莺&middot;杏黄」「日冕光轮」「心情&middot;下雨」「心情&middot;下雪」「心情&middot;气泡」「心情&middot;肯定」「心情&middot;惊叹」「心情&middot;迷惑」</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M4jkdoGJWoTC7vxy3V8cXMVJnof\" data-list=\"bullet\">\n<div><strong>背部配饰：</strong>「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;锈红」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;杏黄」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;白樱」「月舞狐的尾玉&middot;墨玉」</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/11-吟游诗集2 728x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-AtqidmGrzoUFDHxVjiucnlQqnTc\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-RR3zd7vHaoNoF0xc7lXcPiyTnrM\"><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52); font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>【吟游诗集&middot;星芒颂II】上架</strong></span></h4>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Bs9idVIDBoE8vwxy7DdcIkYqnQd\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PWP3dZazDoois4xe9rycRjTEneb\">※ 解锁【典藏诗集】即可获得「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」*1!</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Zs4ldI231onXqDxzS8Vcb9Benid\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JJqsd5M9ToxVPzxMgMVcFYiinOe\"><strong>【开启时间】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JfaldzfLPoHlqSx6R8CcamyEnih\">2025年11月25日 05:00 ~ 2025年12月23日04:59（UTC+8）</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JTGEdkbdZoIY8lxG9guclWUrnkc\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A6CRdLKUcoamcJxLAqWc8c0lnGh\"><strong>【吟游诗集说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TCf5dNms3oNVqKxhjUXcKS1Hndb\">&bull; 活动期间，狩月人可通过完成吟游诗集的见闻任务提升诗歌段落等级，领取丰厚奖励。每期吟游诗集开启后，将默认解锁平装诗集。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VJcrdnrVsoTvpuxqPNgcOUFsnng\">&bull; 解锁【精装诗集】并提升诗歌段落等级可获得「自选魔灵」、「月石」、「华彩沙漏」、「移转模块」、「武器移转模块」、「暮夜的履迹」、「委托手册」、「深红凝珠」等奖励。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ZJnhdnViiojezgxRb14cza3lnek\">&bull; 解锁【典藏诗集】，除以上奖励外，可立即提升10级诗歌段落等级，还可额外获得「月石」*200、「委托手册&middot;三」*5以及「启航自选形象礼箱&middot;星芒」*1奖励！</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-PvZrdICdAo5fOExMmfscAMPbnyg\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vowsd5Halo2yMsxuzQHcDhZdnSh\"><strong>【启航自选形象奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QNtEd0UYPopb0rx9ILGcOmLBnQe\">获得形象自选箱后，可在【背包】-【消耗品】中开启，</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SUUQd3coEovlErx1AK3cm4cbncg\">开启时可从贝蕾妮卡、幻景、莉兹贝尔、妮弗尔夫人、菲娜、丽蓓卡、塔比瑟、琳恩、耶尔与奥利弗、海尔法、玛尔洁、黎瑟、兰迪、西比尔、松露与榛子、奥特赛德、赛琪、达芙涅中自选一套角色形象。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JQF7dliQQo9UEbxgjMXcrQwdncf\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K9ZhdBzI9oit1VxAgxdcuwfwnPf\"><strong>【自选魔灵奖励说明】</strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-YasadQ4Xvoqja1xHfO4cI7dUnhg\">吟游诗集达到30级并解锁【精装诗集】或【典藏诗集】，可从以下五星魔灵中自选召唤一只：「堇青艾尔芙」、「碧玺艾尔芙」、「玛瑙艾尔芙」、「紫晶艾尔芙」、「黑曜艾尔芙」、「欧泊艾尔芙」。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">召唤魔灵后，可在【整备】-【魔灵】界面进行查看和装配。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/12-月卡头像框-菲娜.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 153, 52); font-size: 14pt;\">【侍者皎皎的月度订单】说明</span></strong></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">\n<div data-page-id=\"SjbXdM7OloauTVxgdf6c9W8Anng\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4mQC5j82T4SchvEvcTmtsq\">&bull; 首次购买「侍者皎皎的月度订单」可立即获得当期专属头像框、300月石晶胚、1本委托手册&middot;四，同时订单签约生效时间延长30日。重复购买可增加30天签约时长，在新的一期「月度订单」开启后若签约有效时间大于等于30天，将会获得新一期的「月度订单」限定头像框。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-IhzWdppgoozIsgx25GkcDvg1n1b\">\n<div data-page-id=\"Q9y7dYKj8oc7TsxhRs5cQdPXngd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-To9idhqVropKOfxcAmOcgL5KnOY\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，每日登录游戏可领取90月石，1本委托手册&middot;二，每日凌晨5点重置。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-X50UdF7POoGAhbxhnXKcqoGgn5c\">&bull; 在订单生效期间，因为未登录游戏而未领取的月石、委托手册，不会返还。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EocodPXhVojMiyxzjSOcp62MnNc\">&bull; 月度订单的签约生效时间小于90天时，才可继续购买并正常增加生效时长。</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
