                ["language"] = "CN",
                ["body"] = "<div data-page-id=\"DG0NddktIoUQKqxuKXscuuPlnle\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvNs7Z2PUjkCJEvFCDy3r7c\"><img src=\"http://pan01-cdn-dna-ali.shyxhy.com/upload/728x200_密函轮换预告_扶疏.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"200\"></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnvNs7Z2PUjkCJEvFCDy3r7c\">委托密函将于2025年12月23日 更新后进行轮换，以下为轮换规则。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcndageZsN2ekyT8IU1dXBeed\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4s1KTYTjyGn0pCjLslXxbg\">2025年12月23日 更新后：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnWXkgj2nCZmWr1e9zNCBHTh\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：扶疏」「密函：泽世的慈雨」</strong></span>将替换<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」</strong></span>进入沉浸式戏剧的限时奖励中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnAZ63fGgxoyEGQN5ubVdMGw\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」</strong></span>将替换<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：莉兹贝尔」</span></strong>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnD0qD2AtDggzV6AnuuHgWrc\">&bull;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\">「密函：织梦的白羽</span>」</strong>将替换<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：引浪小调」</span></strong>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K8EMd8bYloXf2Exwhtjc5zdOnPc\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：雀舞云屏」</strong></span>将替换<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\">「密函：茵布拉花序」</span></strong>加入梦魇残声挑战奖励中；</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnl6ZtPNgxKOFlHzzOvKFtYb\">&bull;<span style=\"color: rgb(218, 42, 74);\"><strong>「密函：莉兹贝尔」「密函：引浪小调」「密函：茵布拉花序」</strong></span>将永久加入【委托密函】商店兑换中。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnPNTNDdztJLNY5ci08Rt4rd\">特别提醒：本次梦魇残声奖励轮换时间为12月23日（周二），更新后<strong>不会重置</strong>梦魇残声周奖励次数，若想获取<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\"><strong>「密函：菲娜」「密函：织梦的白羽」「密函：雀舞云屏」</strong></span>的狩月人，请根据自身需求安排游玩挑战。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnkd04xdWnTKrYMZBJMxge3P\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnCbXu6kFP1Gr84VNUNJ83Gg\">随着本次沉浸式戏剧更新，剧目中的【舞台伴奏】与【推荐属性】也会一同进行更新。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnywD53qIdJJh8F3wJnT5dbd\">本期推荐属性：<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 169, 129);\">风属性</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(78, 147, 243);\">水属性</span></div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnuNry2kt8X0EHAlwJIFopef\">本期【舞台伴奏】将会轮换一批新的&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;，以下为【不朽剧目】中部分&ldquo;伴奏&rdquo;：</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn6fMNYbqNvdXTNL4gwmlRhf\">&bull;【抉择变奏：水与风之歌】：敌方单位受到的水属性及风属性伤害提高400%，受到的其他伤害降低50%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcniKNbC3oVQAd8pasVxAPhUE\">&bull;【活跃急板：血战钢铁谷】：友方单位每损失最大生命4.0%的生命，获得1层暴击提高10.0%，持续12秒，最多叠加10层。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Q4vOdNaq4oNJ3wxR3T9cyWKmnBg\">&bull;【激昂行板：救赎的化身】：友方单位受到来自其他友方的治疗时，获得1层攻击速度提高10.0%和技能速度提高5.0%效果，持续10秒，最多叠加6层，满层时，受到伤害时不会产生僵直。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VYnNdvm1KolX4exllyWcX7mdn9g\">&bull;【防御变奏：千锤百炼】：敌方单位受到的单次生命伤害不会超过生命上限的35.0%。</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VYnNdvm1KolX4exllyWcX7mdn9g\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VYnNdvm1KolX4exllyWcX7mdn9g\">\n<div data-page-id=\"DG0NddktIoUQKqxuKXscuuPlnle\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\">\n<div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnttqOiJu7cJB6FyUOtnJPig\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">▍更多【舞台伴奏】可在版本更新后进入游戏内查看。</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
